  EffectDiscription_ENG: "When you would use this card, if you have a green Tamer
    in play, reduce the cost by 1.[Main] 1 of your Digimon gets +5000 DP and gains
    \uFF1CRush\uFF1E for the turn. (This Digimon may attack the turn it was played.)
    Then, 1 of your Digimon may attack your opponent's Digimon."
